e:[["$","title","0",{"children":"Best practices for ISO 9001 Quality Management audit | How to device ISO 9001 certification Quality audit | Wizms"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Best practices for ISO 9001 Quality Management audit\n            Anyone who has had to audit the top management team as a part of an Quality audit can"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"Best practices for ISO 9001 Quality Management audit"}],["$","meta","3",{"property":"og:title","content":"Best practices for ISO 9001 Quality Management audit | How to device ISO 9001 certification Quality audit | Wizms"}],["$","meta","4",{"property":"og:description","content":"Best practices for ISO 9001 Quality Management audit\n            Anyone who has had to audit the top management team as a part of an Quality audit can"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://wizms.net/best-practices-for-iso-9001-quality-management-audit"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:type","content":"article"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"article:published_time","content":"2026-01-02T06:30:36+00:00"}],["$","meta","8",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary"}],["$","meta","9",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Best practices for ISO 9001 Quality Management audit | How to device ISO 9001 certification Quality audit | Wizms"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Best practices for ISO 9001 Quality Management audit\n            Anyone who has had to audit the top management team as a part of an Quality audit can"}],["$","link","11",{"rel":"icon","href":"/favicon.ico"}],["$","$L23","12",{}]]
10:["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 9001 Certification Standard is the key basis for questions"}]
11:["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"When you're auditing your top management team, it's sensible to bear in mind that the clauses of the ISO 9001:2015 certification standard remain the idea of your audit. It may also be useful to make sure that your top team has the audit schedule beforehand. This can enable them time to organize and make sure the correct evidences and reports exists for the audit. These ought to embody queries on, and evidence regarding:"}]
12:["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Context of the organization"}]
13:["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Leadership"}]
14:["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Planning"}]
15:["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Support"}]
16:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Operation"}]
17:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Performance evaluation"}]
18:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Improvement"}]
19:["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Sample Questionnaire"}]
1a:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Prepare some sensible set of questions which will encourage and allow top managers to address the existing problems and issues freely to you. For instance, questions like “What changes have you seen to the organization's structure context and interested party list this year, and the way do you see that have impact on Quality performance within the next year?” will encourage a broader image than simply scrutinizing this year’s interested parties with last."}]
1b:["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"“Can you justify how the management review system works and the way Quality objectives are determined by the top team?” is another valid kind of question."}]
1c:["$","p","18",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Open ended questioning like this could typically illustrate a number of the thought processes the management team employs behind the decisions it makes. Consequently, this illustrates the depth of leadership and management commitment to the problems that are governed by the QMS itself."}]
1d:["$","p","19",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Likewise, an issue like: “How effective do you suppose your Quality risk identification and Quality aspect process is? Are there any major legislative changes on the horizon that will have an effect on the business?” will be massively effective, particularly with international problems like BREXIT in the UK, and therefore the doubts over the trade scenario between China and the USA."}]
1e:["$","p","20",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Address issues in their language"}]
1f:["$","p","21",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"You can realize that talking to top management in a very language they perceive and appreciate will bring advantages to your audit. Highlighting opportunities for improvement typically ends up in reduced price and augmented margin. Prompt the top management that internal auditing could be a positive and cooperative operation where either side will work along to spot gaps, opportunities for improvement and make sure that the corporate QMS and overall performance may be improved as a result."}]
20:["$","p","22",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Fix the Non-conformities"}]
21:["$","p","23",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"You have involved your top management in your audit and have found a non-conformity. Firstly, be discreet and diplomatic. Secondly, keep in mind two things: a non-conformity discovered at internal audit is better than one found by your certification auditor, and it provides a tangible opportunity to boost your management system by playacting an efficient corrective action. This is often the time to prompt yourself and your top management that you simply are both on identical aspect. You all wish an equivalent outcome – an QMS that frequently improves, meets objectives, meets the terms of the ISO 9001 certification standard whereas serving to amplify company profits at the lowest Quality cost. Operating along side your top management in a very cooperative fashion can do this a lot quicker and effectively than before."}]
22:["$","footer",null,{"className":"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"Best practices for ISO 9001 Quality Management audit"}]]}]}]
